ull,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold mb-3","children":"Can Katie handle emergency pest calls at night?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/60 leading-relaxed","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"Absolutely. Katie answers 24/7 including nights, weekends, and bank holidays. She identifies emergency keywords like 'wasp nest', 'rat infestation', 'bed bugs', 'swarm', and 'bites' — then marks the enquiry as emergency priority in your WhatsApp alert. You see it immediately and can respond within minutes, even at 3am."}}]]}],["$","div","3",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold mb-3","children":"What information does Katie collect from pest control customers?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/60 leading-relaxed","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"Katie captures: full name, phone number, postcode, property type (house/flat/commercial/restaurant/hotel), pest type (wasps, rats, mice, bed bugs, cockroaches, fleas, ants, squirrels, pigeons, foxes), infestation severity (single sighting vs full infestation), property size, commercial vs residential, urgency level, and preferred appointment time. For emergencies, she also asks about health risks and access requirements."}}]]}],["$","div","4",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold mb-3","children":"Will customers know they're talking to AI?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/60 leading-relaxed","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"Katie introduces herself as your digital assistant with a natural, professional voice. Most callers appreciate the instant response over voicemail or a ringing phone — especially during panic situations like wasp stings or rat sightings. In user surveys, 89% of callers are satisfied with the AI experience — they just want the pest problem solved fast."}}]]}],"$L59","$L5a","$L5b","$L5c"]}],"$L5d"]}]}]
